title: EastEnders cast fear Danny Dyer will quit the soap after bosses force the party animal actor to take extended break to sort his life out
text:
TV Magazine Don't do one Dyer EastEnders cast fear Danny Dyer will quit the soap after bosses force the party animal actor to take extended break to sort his life out 
Cast and crew say they are worried that party animal actor is on the verge of leaving permanently and bosses are believed to be thinking of ways to write him out Exclusive By DAN WOOTTON, Associate Editor 17th February 2017, 9:52 pm
